# - leopold fc750r pd (white led)
#   - tkl, white backlight, cherry mx brown, pbt keycaps, no rgb.
#   - "adult professional" tkl answer. media on fn layer.
#
# - varmilo va87m (white led)
#   - tkl, white backlight, cherry mx brown, gorgeous pbt keycap themes,
